                    <div class="ml-md-0">
                        <h2 class="mb-4">Welcome to Opabid Farms Limited</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="pb-md-5">
                    <p>
                        Opabid Farm Limited (OFL) is a community interest company organization (your neighborhood farm). Our goal is producing fresh, healthy and affordable staple food item for everyone.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We believe in creating an end to end story about every ingredient on your plate, every meal time of the day. We pride ourselves in the use of scalable and affordable technologies in achieving our set objectives.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        OFL set out to create a sustainable enterprise that focus on feeding the people. We believe that no man should go hungry.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

